{"iti58:0.1":"Itivuttaka 58 ","iti58:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti58:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti58:0.4":"Tanhasutta ","iti58:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti58:2.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, tanha. ","iti58:2.2":"Katama tisso? ","iti58:2.3":"Kamatanha, bhavatanha, vibhavatanha—","iti58:2.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso tanha”ti. ","iti58:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti58:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti58:3.1":"“Tanhayogena samyutta, ","iti58:3.2":"rattacitta bhavabhave; ","iti58:3.3":"Te yogayutta marassa, ","iti58:3.4":"ayogakkhemino jana; ","iti58:3.5":"Satta gacchanti samsaram, ","iti58:3.6":"jatimaranagamino. ","iti58:4.1":"Ye ca tanham pahantvana, ","iti58:4.2":"vitatanha bhavabhave; ","iti58:4.3":"Te ve parangata loke, ","iti58:4.4":"ye patta asavakkhayan”ti. ","iti58:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti58:5.2":"Navamam. "}